        "subject": "LU-18357 doc: fix 'lctl' man page for nodemaps",
        "message": "LU-18357 doc: fix 'lctl' man page for nodemaps\n\nThe `lctl` man page contained some inaccurate information on how\nnodemaps should be used. Further, some nodemap commands were missing\nor were listed incorrectly. This patch fixes these issues.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Marc Vef <mvef@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I17f271fe946a0c0f59f3ed41d0c3b4671289b508\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60191\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Sebastien Buisson <sbuisson@ddn.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
